<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-318-213  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 318 213.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Digital Review  Feb 6 1989 v6 n5 p33(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Ziff-Davis Publishing Co. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Edit package lets users cut, paste on-screen.andO;</TITLE><AUTHOR>Gianatasio, David.andM;</AUTHOR><SUMMARY>Isocom Corp's EZ-Editor allows users to cut and paste from onesession to another, using simple on-screen window functions.andP;  Thetext editor allows several windows to be open at the same time.andO;Users can remove text from any of the sessions and move them intoanother.andP;  Portions of text can be searched throughout the disk andentered into another session.andP;  An automatic save provides regularbackup in user-defined intervals.andP;  The EZ-Editor sessions can alsobe edited through the separate EZ-Modules which perform wordprocessing, translation and syntax checks.andP;  The program runs underUnix, VMS, DOS, AIX and Xenix.andP;  The software is priced from $299for a single user MicroVAX II to $499 for a four-user package.andM;</SUMMARY><DESCRIPT>Company:   Isocom Corp. (products).andO;Product:   EZ-Editor (Utility program).andO;Topic:     Text EditorsMultivendor SystemsUser InterfaceUtility Programs.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Edit Package Lets Users Cut, Paste On-ScreenandM;DALLAS--Cutting, pasting and other editing functions that once requiredscissors, glue and lots of valuable time can now be done on-screen with a neweditorial software package from Isocom, officials said.andM;EZ-Editor lets users perform editing functions on-screen and supports editingacross an unlimited number of sessions.andM;EZ-Editor lets users open many sessions simultaneously under a singleprocess.andP;  Users can remove text from one session and place it in any of theother sessions, or can search directory paths for a desired text andautomatically call up all appropriate files for editing.andP;  The sowftware letsusers toggle between sessions and change their states at will, officialssaid.andM;Also included is an Autor Save/Backup feature that can be programmed to savesessions every one to 99 minutes.andP;  In addition, the package provides forutypes of on-line help, including a scrollable help display across the top ofthe screen.andM;Isocom's EZ-Moduels, which boast word processing, language translation andsyntax checking capabilities, can be used in conjunction with EZ-Editor,officials said.andM;EZ-Editor runs under most operating systems, including Unix, VMS, DOS, AIXand Xenix.andP;  It runs on DEC, IBM, Apollo, ATandamp;T, Sun and Astra platforms.andM;Available now, EZ-Editor is priced from $299 for a single-user Micro VAX IIlicense to $499 for four users.andP;  Isocom is running a special offer throughthe third week of March, during which a MicroVAX II license will range from$149.50 to $249.50.andM;For more information, Isocom Corp. can be contacted at Box 801825, Dallas, TX75380, (214) 490-8288.andO;</TEXT></DOC>